Template: __SHARED_PACKAGE__/db_conn
Type: select
Choices: unix, tcp
Default: unix
Description: Choose the method to connect to your PostgreSQL server.

Template: __SHARED_PACKAGE__/db_host
Type: string
Default: localhost
Description: Enter the hostname or IP address of your PostgreSQL server.

Template: __SHARED_PACKAGE__/db_port
Type: string
Default: 5432
Description: Specify the port number your PostgreSQL server is using.

Template: __SHARED_PACKAGE__/db_user
Type: string
Default: postgres
Description: Enter the username that has the necessary privileges to add users and
 create databases.

Template: __SHARED_PACKAGE__/db_pass
Type: password
Description: Provide the password for the specified PostgreSQL user.
